 "status": "PROPOSED",
 "description": "Standardized P&C ontology for Policy Administration, Claims Management, and Billing, plus shared concepts. v1.1: enriched with concept types, physical name variants, LOB applicability, privacy sensitivity, temporality (drives Silver history treatment), typical attributes, status values, and steward notes. Synthetic learning content; not derived from licensed material.",
